						<summary>

						<p><hi rend="italic">Beam in the temple of Hanumān.</hi></p>						

						<p><hi rend="bold">A.D. 1768.</hi></p>						

						<p>This inscription which is in Nāgarī characters and Sanskrit language records, the installation of god <hi rend="bold">Hanumān</hi> at <hi rend="bold">Sōmāpura</hi> by a certain <hi rend="bold">Dēvarāya</hi> in <hi rend="bold">Śaka 1690, Sarvadhāri, Vaiśākha śu. Trayōdaśi, Friday</hi> corresponding to <hi rend="bold">A.D. 1768 April 29, Friday.</hi></p>						

